spec_data.Name: texlive-e-french
spec_data.Description:
E-french is a distribution that keeps alive the work of Bernard
Gaulle (now deceased), under a free licence. It replaces the
the old "full" frenchpro (the "professional" distribution) and
the light-weight frenchle packages.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:41:40 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Comprehensive LaTeX support for French-language typesetting
